{"tid":1449682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然對家出污糟手段 我哋就更加要利用佢哋","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:06:06.000Z","uid":140335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45c05d38e2cf83b6cadb543982be3986edf7aa87","tid":1449682,"uid":140335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:10.000Z","msg":"現加啲<span style=\"font-size: large;\">恐怖分子</span>已經會偽裝前線<br />\n去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">帶領群眾去衝擊</span></span><br />\n而佢哋帶頭衝擊完之後<br />\n有記者追問呢一班有份衝擊嘅人士身份時<br />\n呢班人只係回應<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我的委任證不需要給全世界人看的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n即係代表 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">衝擊完同記者講 我唔需要出示委任證<br />\n就可以安全離開</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以各位建議以3-4人小隊行動<br />\n做完野之後主動同記者講聲：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察公共關係科會回答你，我正在做事。不要騷擾我們。<br />\n我的委任證不需要給全世界人看的。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n示威者?警察?市民?黑社會?<br />\n邊個知呀?<br />\n搞到現加咁嘅局面係你哋班恐怖分子搞出黎架<br />\n邊個扔磚、邊個放火、邊個打警察、邊個扔國旗、邊個污濁國徽<br />\n無人知，現加全香港嘅市民都知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋班黑警臥底為求逼真，樣樣都有份參與</span></span>"},{"pid":"64fed8bbc2f41e2fcc9903b8c6b6293ec3aa7caa","tid":1449682,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"2019年8月11日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449598</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"86e0566c38d100fde8907d6de0be37780cd023c2","tid":1449682,"uid":156781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"推得過。"},{"pid":"71db0a9018919e7b690d25d90ee379859ed6a49a","tid":1449682,"uid":156781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼"}]}